<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <title>About Us</title>
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">

  <!-- Link CSS -->
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/styles/style1.css">
</head>

<body>

  <!-- Page Header -->
  <header>
    <h1>About This Travel Blog</h1>
    <p>
      Travel is more than moving from one place to another —
      it’s about discovering the world and yourself.
    </p>
  </header>

  <hr>

  <!-- About Content -->
  <section class="about-content">
    <p>
      This travel blog was created for explorers, dreamers, and seekers of
      meaningful journeys. We believe travel offers a vital escape from
      daily routines, helping people relax, reflect, and reconnect with
      the beauty of the world.
    </p>

    <p>
      Through stories, guides, and experiences, this blog highlights
      peaceful mountain escapes, relaxing beach destinations, vibrant
      cultures, hidden cafés, and unforgettable food journeys from around
      the globe.
    </p>

    <p>
      Whether you travel for adventure, relaxation, self-discovery, or
      simple curiosity, our goal is to inspire you to explore at your own
      pace and create memories that last a lifetime.
    </p>
  </section>

  <hr>

  <!-- Mission Section -->
  <section class="about-mission">
    <h2>Our Mission</h2>

    <ul>
      <li>Inspire mindful and meaningful travel experiences</li>
      <li>Encourage exploration beyond tourist paths</li>
      <li>Promote balance between adventure and relaxation</li>
      <li>Share practical tips for stress-free travel</li>
    </ul>
  </section>

  <hr>

  <!-- Closing -->
  <section class="about-closing">
    <p>
      Travel isn’t about escaping life —
      it’s about seeing life with a fresh perspective.
      Thank you for being part of this journey.
    </p>
  </section>

  <hr>

  <!-- Footer -->
  <footer>
    <p>&copy; <%= new Date().getFullYear() %> Travel Blog. All rights reserved.</p>
  </footer>

